summary:
I am currently pursuing a degree in International Business at Fontys University of Applied Science as a highly ambitious and driven individual. I've built a solid reputation as a skilled and engaging team player because of my great communication and networking skills.

I thrive in dynamic, fast-paced workplaces and am always looking for new challenges to help me improve my skills and abilities. My natural curiosity and drive to learn have enabled me to remain adaptable and agile in the face of change, allowing me to flourish in a variety of contexts.
